    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "2404\n2404",
      "Boeing 707-3J6B \"Intercontinental\" B-2404,\npowered by 4 Pratt \u0026 Whitney JT3D-7 Turbo Fan\nEngines, in the colors of CAAC of the Peoples\nRepublic of China. The Chinese characters on\nthe aircraft read \"CAAC,\" for the Civil Aviation\nAdministration of China. The aircraft is shown on\npre-delivery\ntest\nflight over the\nspectacular\nPuget Sound region in beautiful Washington State.\nPhoto courtesy The Boeing Company\nPublished exclusively by:\nAVIATION COLOR PHOTO (ACP)\n2218 North Junett\nTacoma, WA. 98406 USA\nS-034\nAnother AVIATION COLOR PHOTO Quality Post Card\n149183\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\nPOST CARD\nAddress\n2001.082.224"
    ],
